</template>

export default {
	data() {

            {
                label: 'Каталог',

            {
                label: 'Личный кабинет',
                icon: 'pi pi-user',
                to: '/profile',
                style: "font-size: 20px; font-family: Roboto;"
            }
            ]
		}
	}
}
</script>
